txt.en:
Welcome to Lord of the Rings Online! You have created a level 20 character. Congratulations! A number of skills have been slotted for you as well as a number of skills trained but not slotted. To look at all your known skills, use the <rgb=#FFFF00>K</rgb> key.  

We have also advanced and completed several of your quests and granted you traits. Press 'J' if you want to reslot any traits or see which ones are slotted.

 Shortly, you will be pointed towards quest content more appropriate to your level. Take the horse route offered you and be on your way. We hope you enjoy the journey!
